<h4>xx/xx/2019 - 0.35</h4>
<ul>
    <li>Experimental checkin and geocache post type</li>
    <li>Allow to override the publish date, default to 'now'</li>
    <li>UX improvements: (local) draft and publish widget, tags and syndication</li>
    <li>Allow to monitor channels in background and get notification for new posts</li>
    <li>All post types can now be saved as draft, including all properties. This also includes
    coordinates for instance, so you can finish the post later on a different location.</li>
</ul>
<h4>26/02/2019 - 0.34</h4>
<ul>
    <li>Fix crash in post list on update button</li>
</ul>
<h4>25/02/2019 - 0.33</h4>
<ul>
    <li>Optimize post forms (size, color, etc ..)</li>
    <li>Check for visibility property in q=geo call</li>
    <li>Allow to delete an image in preview when creating a post</li>
    <li>Update documentation for width and height of image resize</li>
</ul>
<h4>22/02/2019 - 0.32</h4>
<ul>
    <li>Fix date display in posts</li>
    <li>Add preview screen for a feed</li>
    <li>Use navigation drawer layout for better UX</li>
    <li>Allow selecting and uploading multiple images</li>
    <li>Show account information in header (name and avatar)</li>
    <li>Allow exposing the upload form as an direct share intent</li>
    <li>Allow sharing the url of a post with another application</li>
    <li>Allow to expose a feed share intent to directly add a feed</li>
    <li>Rename 'experimental' keys internally. Reconfigure if needed</li>
    <li>Better account management from within the app (sync, add, delete)</li>
    <li>Add map icon to open map application and ability to show static map on checkin type</li>
</ul>
