<h4>14/01/2019 - 0.27</h4>
<ul>
    <li>Optimize name and text content</li>
    <li>Animated gifs now work in the gallery view too</li>
    <li>Do not crash when zooming on image in gallery</li>
    <li>Developer: settings to view the JSON response of post list</li>
    <li>Render reference content for replies, likes and reposts if available</li>
    <li>Trim content so less space is used for a single reader item</li>
    <li>Scroll back to item row in reader when 'close' button is toggled</li>
    <li>Allow sending a title for a file uploaded to the media endpoint</li>
    <li>Hide post types if not supported or enabled on the micropub server</li>
    <li>If scaling is disabled, use the default preview size of 1000 so the phone does not run out of memory</li>
</ul>
<h4>9/12/2018 - 0.26</h4>
